{"tid":399390,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（吉野家牛肉麵早餐）轉左麵底，好食左好多","createTime":"2017-09-14T01:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T07:54:29.000Z","uid":28195,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe98b1157d3e7c3555466dd0471cc33bce550fc","tid":399390,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"以前既吉野家牛肉麵早餐係用公仔麵，d阿姐煮到好淋，狗都唔屌<br />\n<br />\n近排食左好多日Mos Burger早餐，好喇，俾個機會吉野妹就食佢個牛肉麵早餐<br />\n<br />\n今次發現麵底轉左：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/PotableBlushingIberianchiffchaff-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FPotableBlushingIberianchiffchaff-size_restricted.gif&h=dd55ff3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麵有碗蓋噤住，焗到幾淋自已決定<br />\n<br />\n個麵食落有d似日本既日清雞皇元祖麵，仲無咁鹹，幾好味，加凍飲都俾$28，OK喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/wb/images/1B66D886CC2564DC0AF50CF713451745911A183E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fwb%2Fimages%2F1B66D886CC2564DC0AF50CF713451745911A183E&h=cb7a8ff9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5416a0d9ff6d2ef93ab7de8073464d734a31cefc","tid":399390,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebdbd3348753912a51e4280a09bd9538b3c741e","tid":399390,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"同大快活一樣 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853978e45d4aa6b947d69f65b7c0ea48530ce56b","tid":399390,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同大快活一樣 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"